overview: The PAW Patrol pups are back with daring new rescues and a new puppy crew member in PAW Patrol: Meet Everest! Fan-favorite Everest and high-flying rescue pup Skye embark on daring missions through the snow and ice to rescue their friends, protect stranded animals and guard their community!
tagline: The PAW Patrol pups are back with daring new rescues and a new puppy crew member in PAW Patrol: Meet Everest!
title: Paw Patrol: Meet Everest
